        Changelog
        =========
        
        0.3.0 (2015-01-15)
        ------------------
        
        - Add plone.multilingualbehavior behavior, cktemplate is translable now.
          [bsuttor]
        
        
        0.2.4 (2014-11-05)
        ------------------
        
        - Move unindex ckeditorfolder to setup installation instead of upgrade step.
          [bsuttor]
        
        
